Detailed Description

cvmx_usbn::_dma0_outb_chn5

USBN_DMA0_OUTB_CHN5 = USBN's Outbound DMA for USB0 Channel5

Contains the starting address for use when USB0 reads from L2C via Channel5. Writing of this register sets the base address.
